	} <ref refid="linker-tool-gcc_8h_1a9250789b7dcbb7afd371010fb3a6031d" kindref="member">GROUP_LINK_IN</ref>(ROMABLE_REGION)</initializer>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Define a garbage collectable read-only iterable section output. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Define an output section which will set up an iterable area of equally-sized data structures. For use with <ref refid="group__iterable__section__apis_1ga9104f42cbe4a67a931bed7f7cc8f600f" kindref="member">STRUCT_SECTION_ITERABLE()</ref>. Input sections will be sorted by name, per ld&apos;s SORT_BY_NAME.</para>
<para>This macro should be used for read-only data.</para>
<para>Note that the symbols within the section can be garbage collected. </para>
        </detaileddescription>
        <inbodydescription>
        </inbodydescription>
