        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Helper macro to give extern for start of iterable section. The macro typically will be called <ref refid="group__iterable__section__apis_1ga40c6ba05d5bcb848a530bdc17bbff5be" kindref="member">TYPE_SECTION_START_EXTERN(struct foobar, foobar)</ref>. This allows the macro to hand different types as well as cases where the type and section name may differ.</para>
